For the next run, it is crucial to ensure that the dataset's labels are correctly indexed and loaded. This can be achieved by reviewing the dataset creation and preprocessing steps to confirm that all indices align properly. Additionally, implementing error handling around data loading could help identify and resolve issues early in the training process.